OL,5, Family members of a teenage boy who    
OL,6, drowned were beaten, urinated on and   
OL,7, run over in the lead up to his death,  
OL,8, an inquest has heard.                  
OL,10,FThe mother of Christopher Kapessa said 
OL,11,Fthe family had been subjected to years 
OL,12,Fof racial abuse since moving to Wales. 
OL,14,FShe added that the family received hate
OL,15,Fmail and had their home in Rhondda     
OL,16,FCynon Taf daubed in racist graffiti.   
OL,18,FChristopher, 13, died after being      
OL,19,Fpushed into the river Cynon in 2019.   
